org.zodiark.protocol

Class Envelope

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.zodiark.protocol.Envelope

  • public class Envelope
extends Object
    An Envelope is the vehicule for exchanging data between Zodiark's Endpoint. All communication must be serialized using an Envelope.
